    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a well-maintained, reliable premium car. The exterior retains its original shine, showing only minor, expected road wear such as small stone chips on the front bumper. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and smoke-free; the leather seating is supple with no cracks or tears, and all interior electronics\u2014including the navigation system and dual-zone climate control\u2014are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health with a documented service history. It has recently undergone a full multi-point inspection, receiving new brake pads and a synthetic oil change. The engine runs quietly, and the transmission provides smooth, responsive gear changes. Equipped with tires that have significant tread remaining, this car is ready for the road with no immediate maintenance required. It is a solid, honest example of a cared-for vehicle.",
